.DT
describe
Discworld player help
describe

Name
.SI 5
describe - set your description
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
describe clear
describe edit
describe [description]
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
The describe command is used to put a line about you in your long description
that players get when they look at you.  Describe with no parameters will
print your current description.  Describe clear will clear your description.

Describe edit will drop you into the editor you have chosen and allows you
to edit your description.
.EP

Examples:
.SI 5
describe is a burly looking man with a tattoo.
describe
describe clear
.EI

See also
.SI 5
chfn, look, editor
.EI
